node.text: What I miss? Traveling. The ability to search for cheap tickets and plan adventures, even domestic ones (First world problems, I know). With no end in sight, I actually unpacked and stored my suitcase. My wings are clipped, but for good reason. Asthma has been acting up the last few days which immediately reminded me that I’m no good at being sick and have zero tolerance for pain. My ass is staying in the house and so should you. In the meantime, sharing some old travel photos and dreaming of gulab jamun. #india #tajmahal #nomadnesstribe
